Lightly mix together turkey, 1/3 cup crushed pineapple and next three ingredients. Shape mixture into four burgers. Mix together all Tropical Salsa ingredients in a small bowl. Set aside. Grill burgers over medium heat or in nonstick skillet for 5-6 minutes per side or until done. (165 degrees F internal temperature). Place on hamburger rolls. Top with Tropical Salsa and lettuce.